name: Raiden Ei Speech Synthesizer / Voice Generator
name_original: Raiden Ei Speech Synthesizer / Voice Generator
description:
Alt Download (Backup): https://mega.nz/file/FowSCDAa#CcaFyPirDSFSnGocjPB85i6EKcxFGfV3cf11xQTkojg

Voice Synthesizer / Speech Cloner for Raiden Ei (Raiden Shogun / "Baal" / Beelzebul), the Electro Archon of Inazuma from the video game Genshin Impact by Mihoyo.

Application was made using TensorVox. Enter in the text you want, and an audio file will be generated of Raiden Ei saying the words you put in.
